    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Validation against three bench experiments at the nominal operating point (4.5 L/min, 3000 RPM) consistently demonstrates CFD prediction of RH within 10% of measured values. These results confirm that the model is validated for the full operating range of five flow-speed combinations specified in the COU, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied. The model is therefore accepted as sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision for the Class II CPB device.",
